Description: Shen whole-brain parcellation of 268 functional nodes for the
    'ggseg' ecosystem. Provides a unified 'ggseg_atlas' object with both 2D
    polygon geometry and 3D vertex indices, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
